No, thanks.

03:21.342 --> 03:23.177
You and Jay got divorced?

03:23.177 --> 03:24.378
I kicked him out
a week ago,

03:24.378 --> 03:26.213
but we've been texting.

03:26.213 --> 03:27.915
He's really mean with emojis.

03:27.915 --> 03:31.085
Sometimes it's just, like,
a fist and a skull

03:31.085 --> 03:33.387
and a barrel. What do you
think that barrel means?

03:33.387 --> 03:35.489
Maybe that's where
he's gonna put the body?

03:35.489 --> 03:37.158
Ooh. Maybe.

03:37.158 --> 03:40.461
Yeah. Anyway, um...
enjoy your party.

03:40.461 --> 03:43.598
I'm sure I'll write a comment
about how nice your hair looked.

03:43.598 --> 03:46.334
Stacy, if I was having a party,
you would be invited.

03:46.334 --> 03:48.069
We're friends.

03:48.069 --> 03:49.470
(sighs)

03:49.470 --> 03:51.138
That's what I thought.

03:51.138 --> 03:53.107
RUSS:
<i>Stacy is</i>

03:53.107 --> 03:54.275
