03:54.275 --> 03:56.477
The crazy one?
LINA:
Yeah.

03:56.477 --> 03:58.045
I like her, and you know what?

03:58.045 --> 03:59.947
She's no crazier
than any of your friends.

03:59.947 --> 04:02.049
That's fair.

04:02.049 --> 04:03.451
I have nothing to wear.

04:03.451 --> 04:05.920
