want you to throw me a party.

04:09.056 --> 04:10.291
(phone chimes)

04:10.291 --> 04:12.026
Well, I can
throw a party.

04:12.026 --> 04:13.427
Remember my 30th?

04:13.427 --> 04:15.196
Oh, that was
an off night.

04:15.196 --> 04:18.032
Shit.
What?

04:18.032 --> 04:20.167
Donna can't babysit, and I still
haven't heard back from Jordan.

04:20.167 --> 04:21.168
Who is Jordan?

04:21.168 --> 04:22.870
The funky babysitter.

04:22.870 --> 04:25.106
You know the one with
the cool shoes and jackets?

04:25.106 --> 04:26.307
No.

04:26.307 --> 04:28.843
What is this?

04:28.843 --> 04:30.344
That's your birthday
present to me.

04:30.344 --> 04:32.179
I got you a watch?

04:34.281 --> 04:36.050
Well, should I wrap it?

04:36.050 --> 04:37.284
Ah, what's the point?

04:37.284 --> 04:38.986
Okay, so, wait.

04:38.986 --> 04:42.223
Stacy is throwing the party,
you got your own gift.

04:42.223 --> 04:44.358
I mean, I feel like
something's wrong here.

04:44.358 --> 04:46.060
I'm low-maintenance.

04:46.060 --> 04:47.862
That's what you love about me.

04:47.862 --> 04:50.531
If I was blowing this,
you would say something, right?

04:50.531 --> 04:52.266
Probably not.

05:02.376 --> 05:04.412
