05:31.102 --> 05:32.336
Every month, a new
pair of shoes would come.

05:32.336 --> 05:33.471
She'd model them for me.

05:33.471 --> 05:35.506
Take 'em off,
put 'em on.

05:35.506 --> 05:37.542
