05:37.542 --> 05:39.877
put 'em on.

05:39.877 --> 05:41.212
Feet, right?

05:41.212 --> 05:43.981
Maybe, if I was
as good of a husband

05:43.981 --> 05:47.885
as I was a boyfriend,
I might still be married.

05:47.885 --> 05:51.589
But instead, I'm divorced,
sober and celibate.

05:51.589 --> 05:53.524
The big three.
Hmm.

05:53.524 --> 05:54.959
What changed?

05:54.959 --> 05:56.227
Roxanne was always
so organized.

05:56.227 --> 05:58.096
On top of everything.

05:58.096 --> 06:00.331
The longer we were together,
the less I did.

06:00.331 --> 06:02.900
After a while, she realized
she didn't need me.

06:02.900 --> 06:04.102
Yeah, I feel that.

06:04.102 --> 06:06.904
I'm not even on the Evite.

06:06.904 --> 06:08.072
What?
Really?

06:08.072 --> 06:09.307
Yeah. For the party.

06:09.307 --> 06:10.508
I'm not even on the Evite.

06:10.508 --> 06:12.009
Wow.

06:12.009 --> 06:13.244
Can I give you
a piece of advice?

06:13.244 --> 06:15.213
Is it about feet?
When your wife says

06:15.213 --> 06:16.547
she doesn't
need anything,

06:16.547 --> 06:18.282
don't believe her.
Yeah.

06:18.282 --> 06:19.550
I never believe a word

06:19.550 --> 06:21.953
that comes out
of Cindy's mouth.

06:21.953 --> 06:23.955
