at your house like this,

06:47.575 --> 06:49.577
but you weren't responding
to my text messages,

06:49.577 --> 06:51.846
and then I drove by,
and I saw

06:51.846 --> 06:54.282
your car in the driveway,
so I thought...

06:54.282 --> 06:56.618
