07:04.315 --> 07:05.516
JORDAN:
Not at all.

07:05.516 --> 07:07.351
I've been meaning
to come by

07:07.351 --> 07:09.020
and say good-bye
to the girls anyway.

07:09.020 --> 07:10.988
Good-bye?
Uh, yeah.

07:10.988 --> 07:12.189
