07:27.405 --> 07:29.573
Sure.

07:37.281 --> 07:38.716
(doorbell rings)

07:40.551 --> 07:41.986
Hey there.
Hey.

07:41.986 --> 07:43.454
You're early.

07:43.454 --> 07:44.689
I figured I'd come
a little early, you know.

07:44.689 --> 07:46.324
Lend a hand
for the party tonight.

07:46.324 --> 07:47.325
Oh.

07:47.325 --> 07:48.526
That's great.
Yeah.

07:48.526 --> 07:50.995
Um, I just,
I don't think the balloons

07:50.995 --> 07:52.196
are such a good idea.

07:52.196 --> 07:54.131
What?

07:54.131 --> 07:55.333
Come on, they're festive.

07:55.333 --> 07:56.534
A lot of people

07:56.534 --> 07:58.269
are afraid of balloons.

07:58.269 --> 08:01.072
Balloons and plungers. Right?

08:01.072 --> 08:04.542
I don't know anybody
afraid of balloons or plungers.

08:04.542 --> 08:06.243
We should have dance battles.

08:06.243 --> 08:09.280
Can you arrange
one of those?

08:09.280 --> 08:10.481
