right there.
Okay.

08:54.959 --> 08:57.361
You didn't tell my assistant
I'm separated, did you?

08:57.361 --> 08:58.562
Uh, no.

08:58.562 --> 08:59.628
I didn't say anything.

08:59.628 --> 09:01.232
I don't know anything.

09:01.232 --> 09:03.300
You sure?
Yeah, pretty sure.

09:03.300 --> 09:05.236
People talk.

09:05.236 --> 09:07.204
(sighs)

09:07.204 --> 09:08.639
Hey, guys.

09:08.639 --> 09:10.107
You a history buff?

09:10.107 --> 09:11.675
I guess.

09:16.680 --> 09:19.483
General William
Tecumseh Sherman.

09:19.483 --> 09:21.419
Wow.
Yeah.

09:21.419 --> 09:23.254
The Civil War.

09:23.254 --> 09:25.222
Right. Got it.

09:25.222 --> 09:27.691
They're all hand-painted.

09:27.691 --> 09:30.261
It's the only reason my marriage
lasted as long as it did.

09:30.261 --> 09:31.729
Helped me tune out the insanity.

09:31.729 --> 09:33.364
