09:52.650 --> 09:54.385
It's like suddenly
I was under review.

09:54.385 --> 09:56.320
Hmm.

09:56.320 --> 09:57.621
That's what it is.

09:57.621 --> 10:00.324
They turn 40,
and you're under review.

10:00.324 --> 10:02.526
You either get tenure,
or you end up sleeping

10:02.526 --> 10:03.727
in your office.

10:03.727 --> 10:05.162
Huh.

10:05.162 --> 10:07.398
Yeah. Yeah, with Lina it's like,

10:07.398 --> 10:09.266
