I was really funny.

10:09.266 --> 10:11.068
You know? I used to,
like, crack her up,

10:11.068 --> 10:12.670
like, all the time.

10:12.670 --> 10:14.271
You are funny.

10:14.271 --> 10:16.340
Thanks.

10:16.340 --> 10:17.975
Yeah. I mean,

10:17.975 --> 10:19.643
there's all these cute
girls where I work,

10:19.643 --> 10:21.745
and I crack them up
all the time.

10:21.745 --> 10:24.381
And then I will come home and
say the same thing to Lina,

10:24.381 --> 10:26.117
and she just
rolls her eyes.

10:26.117 --> 10:27.985
She's heard your best material.

10:29.386 --> 10:31.989
I guess I got to work on
some new shit.

10:31.989 --> 10:33.190
Yeah.

10:37.328 --> 10:39.263
LINA:
Hey, is this something

10:39.263 --> 10:41.665
that someone would wear
to a 40th birthday party?

10:41.665 --> 10:43.567
Uh... I don't know.

10:43.567 --> 10:44.969
I've never been to one.

10:44.969 --> 10:47.204
You're lucky.

10:47.204 --> 10:50.541
Oh, my God, this party
I went to last night was insane.

10:50.541 --> 10:52.009
(laughs)

10:52.009 --> 10:53.444
