10:53.444 --> 10:55.546
I think I might have been first.

10:55.546 --> 10:57.448
(laughs) No wonder the
girls love you so much.

10:57.448 --> 10:58.682
You're fun.

10:58.682 --> 11:00.451
Aw, I love them.

11:00.451 --> 11:03.020
