Ow.

11:42.092 --> 11:43.627
You okay?

11:43.627 --> 11:46.263
Yeah, it's just my neck.

11:46.263 --> 11:48.199
What happened?
The doctor said

11:48.199 --> 11:51.502
that it was just totally
normal for someone my...

11:53.070 --> 11:54.672
